And now for something completely different!

Let's have some fun making art out of stamps - art out of art? So meta!
I ran one of the more popular stamps of the 90s (a commemorative Elvis stamp) through a picture-to-Ascii converter. Let's see the results!

Here's the stamp before the conversion:

And here's the stamp after:
